INSERT INTO `wp_2posts` VALUES (1,1,'2013-10-17 06:53:00','2013-10-17 06:53:00','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','trash','open','open','','hello-world','','','2013-10-17 08:15:49','2013-10-17 08:15:49','',0,'http://waindo.net.id/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2013-10-17 06:53:00','2013-10-17 06:53:00','<content>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"page\">\r\n		<div><span class=\"arrow-down\"></span></div>\r\n		<div id=\"box1\">\r\n			<div class=\"title\">\r\n				<h2>Our Service</h2>\r\n				<span class=\"byline\">Total Solution for Digital Information</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"images/service.jpg\" /><br><br><br>\r\n<section>\r\n<font color=\"#a2a3a3\"><font face=\"calibri\"><font size=\"4\"> \r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Waindo SpecTerra is an Indonesian firm of highly skilled and experienced professionals who believe in only providing the best quality and cost-effective solutions to its clients’ information management needs. Our management and staff understand client requirements and count on their years of practical business and technical experience to assist each client achieve continued success.</p><br>\r\n\r\n<p>Waindo SpecTerra believes that understanding the purpose of a project and grasping the nature of underlying business problems, are the key to provide much better solutions than just pure technical solutions. Our professional consultants posses specific technical expertise and are fully backed up by the resources of the entire firm.</p><br>\r\n\r\n<p>Waindo SpecTerra prides itself on the track records its personnel have achieved in a variety of technical and management positions representing the wide spectrum of various industries and technologies. The firm encourages its dedicated full-time consultants to obtain professional certifications and training, and many have done so.</p><br>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide products and services with the selection, accuracy, and potensial uses all types of geographical dat