 Remote Sensing and the resulting points; lines and areas can be mapped directly with ArcView. ArcGIS can be customized with the Avenue object-oriented scripting language (included with ArGIS) in order to create custom applications, which are very powerful and robust. These extensions include Spatial Analyst, Network Analyst, 3D Analyst and ESRI ArcIMS for GIS on the WEB. Extensions can be purchased separately and are loaded and unloaded on demand, allowing for more efficient use of system resources.\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;strong&gt;3D Analyst&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\n\r\n3D Analyst is the ArcGIS incarnation of ArcInfo’s TIN extension, and more. We can create and visualize 3D surfaces, TINs and generate fly-throughs and perspective views. New 3D shape types allow for true 3D visualization, query and analysis.\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Network Analyst&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\n\r\nNetwork Analyst provides the ability to create and query network themes such as roads and streams. Advanced routing, shortest path/optimum route, most efficient route to hit several stops, service areas, closest facilities, drive time areas and clear route directions. Network analyst is perfect for transportation, logistical analysis, AF/FM stream flow and other linear network applications. Network Analyst is easy to learn and runs on PC and UNIX platforms.\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/content&gt;','Prodoct','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2013-10-17 08:19:00','2013-10-17 08:19:00','',2,'http://waindo.net.id/?p=47',0,'revision','',0),(48,1,'2013-10-17 08:19:10','2013-10-17 08:19:10','&lt;font color=\"#a2a3a3\"&gt;&lt;font face=\"calibri\"&gt;&lt;font size=\"4\"&gt;\r\n\r\nGeography Information System&lt;br&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Waindo SpecTerra’s multi-disciplinary staff offer