13-10-17 10:15:19','<content>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"page\">\r\n		<div><span class=\"arrow-down\"></span></div>\r\n		<div id=\"box1\">\r\n			<div class=\"title\">\r\n				<h2>Our Product</h2>\r\n				<span class=\"byline\">Total Solution for Digital Information</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n<img src=\"images/product.jpg\" /><br><br><br>\r\n<font color=\"#a2a3a3\"><font face=\"calibri\"><font size=\"4\"> \r\nGeography Information System<br>\r\n<p>Waindo SpecTerra’s multi-disciplinary staff offer specialist GIS expertise and have executed numerous projects world-wide involving spatial data management.</p>\r\n<p>Waindo SpecTerra offering the entire line of ESRI Desktop GIS products including ArcGIS and the powerful new ArcGIS extensions: Spatial Analyst, Network Analyst, Internet Map Server, 3D Analyst, Streetmap and ArcPress for ArcGIS. Other complementary ESRI Desktop GIS products are offered such as the Data Automation Kit and ArcCAD (Environmental Systems Research Institute, Redlands, CA).</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong>ArcGIS Desktop</strong>\r\n<br>\r\nArcGIS is the most popular and user-friendly GIS product in the world. ArcGIS can be used to view, query and produce maps from existing GIS data. New geographic data can also be created with ArcView from existing tabular databases or by digitizing of graphic elements. Field data can be collected with Remote Sensing and the resulting points; lines and areas can be mapped directly with ArcView. ArcGIS can be customized with the Avenue object-oriented scripting language (included with ArGIS) in order to create custom applications, which are very powerful and robust. These extensions include Spatial Analyst, Network Analyst, 3D Analyst and ESRI ArcIMS for GIS on the WEB. Extensions can be purchased separately and are loaded and unloaded on demand, allowing for more efficient use of system resources.\r\n</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong>3D Analyst</strong>\r\n<br>\r\n3D Analyst is the ArcGIS incarnation of ArcInfo’s TIN extension, and more. We can create and visualize 3D surfaces, TINs and generate fly-throughs and perspective views. New 3D shape types allow for true 3D visualization, query and analysis.\r\n</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong>Network Analyst</strong>\r\n<br>\r\nNetwork Analyst provides the ability to create and query network themes such as roads and streams. Advanced routing, shortest path/optimum route, most efficient route to hit several stops, service areas, closest facilities, drive time areas and clear route directions. Network analyst is perfect for transportation, logistical analysis, AF/FM stream flow and other linear network applications. Network Analyst is easy to learn and runs on PC and UNIX platforms.\r\n</p>\r\n</font></font></font></font>\r\n</section>\r\n		</div>\r\n</content>\r\n','Product','','inherit','open','open','','56-revision-v1','','','2013-10-17 17:15:19','2013-10-17 10:15:19','',56,'http://waindo.net.id/?p=123',0,'revision','',0),(143,1,'2012-01-28 17:55:34','2012-01-28 10:55:34','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://waindo.net.id/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/404804_275188532548166_1603459534_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-144\" alt=\"404804_275188532548166_1603459534_n\" src=\"http://waindo.net.id/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/404804_275188532548166_1603459534_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"119\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Waindo SpecTerra Indonesia menerima kunjungan 27 mahasiswa plus 2 dosen pendamping Bapak Aryono Prihandito dan Bapak Hadiman dari T. Geodesi Universitas Gajahmada Yogyakarta, ini merupakan sebuah penghormatan dari Jurusan Teknik Geodesi UGM kepada Waindo SpecTerra, bahwa Eksistensinya sebagai sebuah perusahaan Nasional dibidang jasa survei dan pemetaan diperhitungkan. Pak Anto dan Pak Singgih tampak sedang memberikan wejangan kepada adik-adik mahasiswa T. Geodesi UGM dan Kiat-kiat sukses menjalani karir dibidang survei dan pemetaan, sambil berkelakar beberapa yang saya kutip katanya: \" Kalau ingin sukses dibutuhkan 2 hal yang h